    <h3>Description</h3>

      <p>Winnie the Pooh was born in 1914.  He was originally a protege of A.A. Milne, working with Christopher Robin in the entertainment industry from 1926.  In 1966, he went to work for Walt Disney and started in movie-length features.  He remains a big favourite with children of all ages.</p>

    <h3>Project: Finding honey</h3>

    <div class="projects">
      <ol>
        Pooh likes honey and is always looking for more.  He is usually in conflict with honey-bees in their hives.  This project aims to discover new methods of recovering honey from hives without getting stung..
